      <div id="right_content">
        <div class="content_title">International Cooperation Office</div>
        <div class="content_text">
          <div class="layout_2">
            <div id="list_5">
<h3>Introduction</h3>
The international cooperation office is responsible for:      
<ul class="blue_arrow">
<li>Organizing and managing the application for international cooperation projects in scientific research launched by ministries;</li>
<li>Organizing and managing application for the research funds granted by international organizations including foreign universities, institutions, and enterprises;</li>
<li>Negotiating, organizing and managing international cooperation projects in scientific research with international organizations including foreign universities, institutions and enterprises;</li>
<li>Organizing, planning, initiating and managing major international scientific cooperation projects in scientific research;</li>
<li>Establishing and maintaining the information system for international cooperation in science and technology;</li>
<li>Assessing applications for exit approval by all SJTU faculty;</li>
<li>Formulating policies concerning international cooperation in science and technology.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<br />
<h3>Staff</h3>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<p><strong>Xu Lin</strong></p>
<p>Director of the International Cooperation Office</p>
<p>+86 21 34207982</p>
<p>Room B-609, Administration Building</p>
<p><a href="mailto:linxu@sjtu.edu.cn">linxu@sjtu.edu.cn</a></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<p><strong>Duties and Responsibilities</strong></p>
<ul class="blue_arrow">
<li> Assisting in carrying out international cooperation in science and technology;</li>
<li> Organizing and coordinating all the work in the international cooperation office;</li>
<li> Organizing, planning and managing cooperation in scientific research with foreign universities, institutes, and enterprises;</li>
<li> Organizing, planning and managing cooperation in scientific research with transnational enterprises and groups;</li>
<li> Assessing the applications for exit approval of all SJTU faculties;</li>
<li> Formulating policies concerning international cooperation in science and technology;</li>
<li> Completing other work assigned by the leader.</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<p><strong>Li Yinyue</strong></p>
<p>+86 21 34207982</p>
<p>Room B-609, Administration Building</p>
<p><a href="mailto:liyinyue@sjtu.edu.cn">liyinyue@sjtu.edu.cn</a></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<p><strong>Duties and Responsibilities</strong></p>
<ul class="blue_arrow">
<li> Organizing and managing applications for special fund for international cooperation by national ministries and commissions;</li>
<li> Collecting information on international cooperation policies issued by national ministries and commissions and giving feedbacks;</li>
<li> Communicating, contacting and meeting the departments of international cooperation of national ministries and commissions;</li>
<li> Applying, assessing and managing SJTU-UM special funds;</li>
<li> Completing other work assigned by the leader.</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
